snippet: Protesters held rallies in several Egyptian cities on Thursday in opposition to the military’s ouster one year ago of Mohamed Morsi, the country’s first fairly elected president.
abstract: Protesters hold rallies in several Egyptian cities in opposition to the military's ouster of Pres Mohamed Morsi one year earlier.
